Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:23.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kidnapping case with a ransom note...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:24.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This type of case is usually motivated by money.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But today's case is a little abnormal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing through to the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I look like a child, but have the intellect of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:32.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's 2:30 PM, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the time of day when you just want to take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.59,0:02:23.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:27.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, an ambulance! Call an ambulance first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No need for an ambulance...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He died instantaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was speeding, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Serves him right for driving so recklessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:49.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with all this money?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, what is this? A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:59.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The ¥300,000 is all here. The police were not informed."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Please hurry and release my father. Doumoto."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means this money is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A payment so a kidnapper will release their hostage...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A ransom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Kidnapping Case... Or So It Seems!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:28.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The name of the deceased is Hirano Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our records show past arrests for blackmail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that he's the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would appear that he was on his way\Nback from collecting the ransom money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be terrible if he was the only one involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would mean we wouldn't be able to\Nfind where the hostage is being kept, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father has a kidney disease that requires treatment every six hours."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You will find the medicine enclosed with\Nthis letter, so please administer it to him."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This means the hostage won't be getting his medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:05.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry, or his life will be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, where's he being held captive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First of all, we don't even know who\Nthe hostage is, let alone where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are many people with the surname Doumoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't he need to go to the hospital a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To check on his condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika Electronics.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:30.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're here to deliver the television you ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... We didn't order that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There must be some sort of mix-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we're sure we aren't mistaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we need you to come double-check the receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... we never ordered a television.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:53.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's your old college buddy. It's me, remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm his son!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why're you here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bringing a kid along makes us look less suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's been a kidnapping recently, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:15.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We questioned every hospital in the area...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About a "Doumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}" who has a kidney disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were able to identify the hostage as\NDoumoto Shouzaburo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, a patient of Beika City Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:32.50,CharCards03,,0,0,0,,Doumoto Akanari (32)\N\h\hMitsuko's Husband\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:32.50,CharCards04,,0,0,0,,Doumoto Mitsuko (30)\N{\fs13}Shouzaburo's Daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:29.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,But, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:32.81,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We were told that if we reported this\Nto the police, our father would be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the situation has{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ged now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:38.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do the police have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We placed it exactly where we were told to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, the culprit\Ndied in a motorbike accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't abandon hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:53.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're taking this matter very seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're searching for clues that will lead us to your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think that my father didn't get the medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He needs to have an injection every six hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:04.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When was the last time he got one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 9:00 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:10.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,3:00 PM!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's now overdue for his scheduled dosage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:15.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't get sick immediately after missing a dosage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if he doesn't get it within eight hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the absolute limit is eight hours, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deadline is 5:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only an hour and a half left...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:38.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please explain, in detail, how and\Nwhen your father was kidnapped...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As well as the terms you were given.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:42.90,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We have four people in our household.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:44.44,CharCards02,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,0)}Doumoto Shouzaburo (64)\N{\fs9}\h\hDoumoto Metal Company President\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:46.47,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,My father, Shouzaburo, who is the owner\Nand company president of a metal factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His only daughter, myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband, Akinari{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And our housekeeper, Masayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:54.17,CharCards05,,0,0,0,,Sudo Masayo (67)\N{\fs12}Doumoto Family Housekeeper
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:07:00.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone had the day off today to celebrate the\Nfactory's anniversary, thus we were all home at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am also employed at the same factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you're his daughter's husband,\Nyou'd be next in line to succeed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gave Father his injection at 9:00 AM,\Nthen left to visit a friend for several hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had already made plans to go somewhere in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:30.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father left to take a walk around\N9:30 AM, as is his daily routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around 10:00 AM, I retired to my office to finish some filing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:42.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around 11:00 AM, while I was cleaning the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a phone call from a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put a member of the family on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Doumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What? Kidnapped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:08:00.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In short, Doumoto Shouzaburo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was\Nkidnapped between 9:30 AM and 11:00 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's highly probable that he\Nwas kidnapped while on his walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he always take the same route on these walks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, he always takes the same path.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you map it out for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, this might help to figure\Nout where the hostage is located.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, I told my wife to come home as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll gather the ¥300,000 ransom somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as we pay the money, Father will be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do, Akinari{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This should be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akinari{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ransom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as we paid and they confirmed that it\Nwas real, they said they would return Father to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We believed those words...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:29.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We even prepared the medicine just in case!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:33.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,4:00 PM? Only one hour left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't cry. Father will definitely come home safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. Even if he acts like that,\Nlet's keep believing in his safe return.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Kogoro told me to ask you something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you mean by, "Even if he acts like that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:10:03.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Master frequently spoke coldly\Ntowards Akinari{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} and treated him badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spoke coldly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't even recognize the significance of your position?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:15.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been trying my best for the employees' sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I guess you aren't fit to be my successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just looking at your face makes me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:30.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even I don't understand why Master\Nstarted being so strict with Akinari{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But his wife backs him up at times like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:38.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When they first married, they\Nwere always protecting each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But recently, even she treats him poorly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you ashamed of yourself, Dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just going to sit there and take that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Try being a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko, why are you acting like this too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it's her father's influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:58.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, everything{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ged once he was kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even Akinari{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} is praying for his safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:07.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he gathered all that money together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that had nothing to do with this case, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to Hirano Takeshi's friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he'd have a lot of money after\Na "special job" he'd be doing this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must mean he was hired\Nby someone to commit the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, but we don't have\Nany leads as to whom that might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:40.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep asking around. Hopefully, someone will\Nhave useful information relating to this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only we knew who that person was,\Nwe could find out where the hostage is being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means there's an accomplice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But something doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somethings strange, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you were the one that hired\Nsomeone to do this, and he didn't return...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you normally call to see what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:03.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like, "Are you trying to kill the hostage?" or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:05.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't the person in question call him\Nasking why he hadn't brought the ransom money?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the real motive for this kidnapping is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:29.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course! If you think about it this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello again. What do you need, young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Akinari{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} stayed in his office all morning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:38.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. He said he had work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he say anything to you during that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he say something? Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be busy, so I won't be needing any tea, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:53.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:24.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know who the true culprit behind this case is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:28.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, if I try to question him\Ndirectly, he'll come up with an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And during that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:35.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not about the ransom!\NThat's not the culprit's true motive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's 4:30 PM. Only thirty minutes left!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is it? Where is the hostage is being held?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:48.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at a map for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just seeing if I can figure out where the bike was heading.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:57.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obviously, he was going to where the hostage is being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After collecting the ransom, he would've rode\Npast Beika Park and Jikogenba High School and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:08.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that sounds right. But, you know, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if we knew the general direction,\Nit could be 10km or even 100km away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:14.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah-le-le?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a place over here that has\Nthe same name as his other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doumoto Metal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. That's our old factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About half a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We moved to a larger location in East Beika,\Nleaving the old one abandoned ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's an empty factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means nobody would have a reason to go there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, that might be the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That seems very likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, the map, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:41.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So you're saying Father is in that factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:45.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a high possibility that he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:49.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! We only have fifteen minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, please don't lose hope until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good choice of words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only fifteen minutes left.\NWe've got to make it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, time, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give it to me, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:42.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:51.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's still breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:16:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Takagi, please send an ambulance here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:00.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our location is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your wife will be accompanying her father to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir, aren't you going with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:24.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold up a second, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:32.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Kogoro has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:42.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe that Doumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Akinari{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that you wanted the opposite to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The opposite", you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I discovered that the ransom wasn't\Nwhat the kidnapper was after, I figured it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I instructed Conan to ask Masaya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to her, you and your wife,\NMitsuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} were happily married.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, once you were employed\Nas the husband of the boss's daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her father started treating you badly, saying\Nthings like, "I guess you aren't fit to be my successor."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You kept getting scolded by her father,\Nand went through some tough times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obviously, you resented Doumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even to the point of wanting him dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you didn't have the courage to do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when you thought up this scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scheme?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Akinari{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is the culprit, Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was kidnapped while he was on his walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when Akinari{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in my office the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you really working in your office?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before you went into your office,\Nyou told the housekeeper...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be busy, so I won't be needing any tea, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, you left through the window using a\Nspare pair of shoes you had prepared beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You drove up to Doumoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who was in the\Nmiddle of his walk, and asked to speak with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:29.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You even brought me to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:31.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you're the most despicable man I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say, I'll have you know that I won't-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:39.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akinari{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, we have to go back quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have my medicine with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akinari{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}, you have a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kidnapping?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he put on an act for everyone,\Npretending to be oblivious to the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, he made a big mistake in his haste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you look at his window ledge in his office closely...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:22.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll find traces of the same oil found here in this factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The oil is custom-made for this factory, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That serves as evidence that he\Ncame back in through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:31.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also found a discarded tissue he used to wipe off the ledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the biggest piece of evidence are the\Nfootprints he made on the ground as he was leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:42.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It takes approximately one hour to drive\Nbetween the Doumoto residence and this factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's plenty of time to commit the crime, as you\Ngoing to be "in your office" from 10:00 AM to 11:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That certainly is plausible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:53.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, why would he do it himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:57.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it have been simpler\Nto have the person he hired do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:20:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, that man was hired\Nwithout knowing about the kidnapping plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He helped without knowing about the kidnapping?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. He probably said to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:12.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call me between 11:00 AM and 2:00 PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And be sure to pick up a suitcase near Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need to know what's in\Nthe suitcase, so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He knew that if he informed others of\Nhis plan, it might backfire on him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, he planned this specifically for today,\Nwhen his wife would be leaving the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.77,0:20:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Father was kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A suitcase in Beika Park?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:37.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means he was talking to\Nhimself on the phone the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. If Hirano hadn't gotten into an accident,\Nhe would have gotten all his money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything would have went according to his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:21:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There wouldn't have been a\Nneed for the police or a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All he had to do was act like he was worried,\Nand wait until just enough time had passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, you're wrong about the motive, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did indeed hold a grudge against my father-in-law...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also wanted to use the money to\Nshow Mitsuko that I wasn't insensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought if I showed her how\Ndesperate I was to get him back...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She would love me again, just like she used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:47.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, I had come to the riverside of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Imagining a continuation of yesterday's dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:22:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seemed so grown-up when you were a boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say goodbye, so I hid under my umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.53,0:22:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we ever meet again, just please remember
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.21,0:22:19.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,all those times, and don't forget me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My love and affection are things that will never{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.97,0:22:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are my one and only love, and that's how it will always be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.81,0:22:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like many people, I reminisce while holding on to my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:23:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I can keep the memory of us meeting from fading away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Mitsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said Father will have a full recovery!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After he regains consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.30,0:23:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell him how desperate you were to save him...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.10,0:23:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how worried you were about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.56,0:23:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, I'm sure Father won't\Npurposely make you feel bad anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Purposely?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father acted so horribly because he\Nwanted to mold you into a great successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, Father thinks a great deal about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:36.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's always praising your determination and helpfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These past few days, I've been acting just like my father too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really hated doing that, and I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:45.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, Akinari{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.71,0:23:49.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
